### ============================================
### GATEWAY SERVICE (Port 8080)
### ============================================

### Get all albums (via Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums

### Get specific album (via Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/{{albumId}}

### Create new album (via Gateway)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Anthem for the Underdog",
  "artist": "12 Stones",
  "releaseYear": 2007
}

### Update album (via Gateway)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/albums/{{albumId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Anthem for the Underdog (Bonus Track Version)",
  "artist": "12 Stones",
  "releaseYear": 2007
}

### Delete album - will trigger event to delete songs (via Gateway)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/albums/{{albumId}}

### Get all songs from all albums (via Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/songs

### Get songs from specific album (via Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/{{albumId}}/songs

### Get specific song from album (via Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/{{albumId}}/songs/{{songId}}

### Create song in album (via Gateway)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums/{{albumId}}/songs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Lie to Me",
  "durationMinutes": 3
}

### Update song (via Gateway)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/albums/{{albumId}}/songs/{{songId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Lie to Me (acoustic)",
  "durationMinutes": 3
}

### Delete song (via Gateway)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/albums/{{albumId}}/songs/{{songId}}

### Test: Get songs from non-existent album (via Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/songs

### Test: Create song in non-existent album (via Gateway)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/songs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Song",
  "durationMinutes": 3
}

